# Ship Systems Implementation Rules
- Always refer to docs/tech_design.md for:
  - System architecture and class diagrams
  - State machine implementations
  - UI component designs
  - Sequence diagrams for system interactions
  - Component relationships and dependencies

- Always refer to docs/spaceships_spec.md for:
  - Ship class specifications and base stats
  - System upgrade paths and levels
  - Damage mechanics and thresholds
  - Repair mechanics and requirements
  - System interactions and dependencies 